# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  DueDateHQ — root .env  (copy to `.env`, gitignored)                     ║
# ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║  Scope · This file is read by NODE TOOLING ONLY:                         ║
# ║    · pnpm scripts, monorepo CI, `scripts/*.mjs`                          ║
# ║    · drizzle-kit (remote D1 migrations)                                  ║
# ║    · wrangler CLI for `pnpm deploy` / `db:migrate:remote`                ║
# ║    · gitleaks (`pnpm secrets:scan`)                                      ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  ⚠ The Worker RUNTIME does NOT read this file.                           ║
# ║    Secrets that the Worker needs at runtime (AUTH_*, GOOGLE_*, RESEND_*, ║
# ║    VAPID_*, AI_*, SENTRY_DSN, POSTHOG_KEY) must live in:                 ║
# ║      · apps/server/.dev.vars          — local `wrangler dev`             ║
# ║      · `wrangler secret put <NAME>`   — staging / production             ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  ⚠ The SPA (apps/web, Vite) does NOT read this file either.              ║
# ║    Public browser vars must be prefixed `VITE_` and placed in:           ║
# ║      · apps/web/.env.local  (optional; see apps/web/src/lib/env.ts)      ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  The runtime variables below are kept here as a REFERENCE INDEX so that  ║
# ║  everyone can see the full surface in one place. Leave them blank in     ║
# ║  your local `.env` unless a CI/CD step needs them.                       ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# [1] ACTUALLY USED BY ROOT TOOLING — fill these if you run CLI locally
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Cloudflare CLI auth · required for `pnpm deploy`, `pnpm db:migrate:remote`,
# and drizzle-kit remote pushes. NOT read by the Worker at runtime.
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=

# Node process hint for scripts. The Worker uses ENV (see below) instead.
NODE_ENV=development


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# [2] REFERENCE INDEX — Worker runtime secrets
#     ❗ Fill these in apps/server/.dev.vars for local dev,
#        and via `wrangler secret put` for staging/production.
#     Values left here are only used by deploy-time CLI wrappers (if any).
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ───── Cloudflare Bindings (declared in apps/server/wrangler.toml; for docs) ─
# DB           (D1)
# CACHE        (KV)
# RATE_LIMIT   (Rate Limit binding)
# R2_PDF       (R2 bucket)
# R2_MIGRATION (R2 bucket)
# R2_AUDIT     (R2 bucket)
# VECTORS      (Vectorize index)
# EMAIL_QUEUE  (Queues producer)
# ASSETS       (Static Assets binding)

# ───── App ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ENV  · Worker-side environment flag (development | staging | production)
# APP_URL · Origin where the browser-facing SPA lives (Vite in dev, Worker in prod)
ENV=development
APP_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ───── Auth · Better Auth + Google OAuth ─────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH_SECRET · openssl rand -base64 32  (min 32 chars)
# AUTH_URL    · origin of the Worker that serves /api/auth/* (dev: 8787)
AUTH_SECRET=
AUTH_URL=http://localhost:8787
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# ───── LLM (via Cloudflare AI Gateway) ────────────────────────────────────────
AI_GATEWAY_ACCOUNT_ID=
AI_GATEWAY_SLUG=duedatehq
OPENAI_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY=
LANGFUSE_SECRET_KEY=

# ───── Mail (Resend) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
RESEND_API_KEY=
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@duedatehq.com

# ───── Web Push (Phase 1+) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=
VAPID_SUBJECT=mailto:ops@duedatehq.com

# ───── Observability ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SENTRY_DSN=
POSTHOG_KEY=
